result.execSummary:
The defendant Timothy A. Schubbe was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Timothy A. Schubbe is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Timothy A. Schubbe was found guilty of Possession of Methamphetamine, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(g).
